# GitHub Pages

- User site: artifact is repo root (`.`)
- `index.html` required at root; `.nojekyll` disables Jekyll
- Workflow: validate HTML → upload-pages-artifact → deploy-pages@v4
- Deploy job needs `pages: write` + `id-token: write`
- `concurrency: cancel-in-progress: false`
- Push to `main` triggers deploy — **only when user explicitly asks to push/deploy**
- Do not commit or push unless the user asks
- One-time: Settings → Pages → GitHub Actions source
- Verify: `gh run list --workflow pages.yml`
